届年度仪式将于2月18日在纽卡斯尔举行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spice-krept-konan-and-bashy-announced-as-mobo-2025-performers-3830321">Krept＆Konan和Bashy的Spice Post宣布，Mobo 2025表演者</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Spice-Krept-Konan-and-Bashy.-CREDIT_-Paras-Griffin_Getty-Images-Gareth-Cattermole_Getty-Images-and-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Forbes-Family-Group.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Spice-Krept-Konan-and-Bashy.-CREDIT_-Paras-Griffin_Getty-Images-Gareth-Cattermole_Getty-Images-and-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Forbes-Family-Group.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Spice-Krept-Konan-and-Bashy.-CREDIT_-Paras-Griffin_Getty-Images-Gareth-Cattermole_Getty-Images-and-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Forbes-Family-Group-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Spice-Krept-Konan-and-Bashy.-CREDIT_-Paras-Griffin_Getty-Images-Gareth-Cattermole_Getty-Images-and-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Forbes-Family-Group-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Spice-Krept-Konan-and-Bashy.-CREDIT_-Paras-Griffin_Getty-Images-Gareth-Cattermole_Getty-Images-and-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Forbes-Family-Group-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Spice-Krept-Konan-and-Bashy.-CREDIT_-Paras-Griffin_Getty-Images-Gareth-Cattermole_Getty-Images-and-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Forbes-Family-Group-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Spice-Krept-Konan-and-Bashy.-CREDIT_-Paras-Griffin_Getty-Images-Gareth-Cattermole_Getty-Images-and-Dave-Benett_Getty-Images-for-Forbes-Family-Group-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Spice， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/krept-and-konan">Krept＆Konan</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bashy">Bashy</a>将在2025年MOBO奖中演出。在下面找到更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mobo-founder-kanya-king-interview-alternative-dance-jamal-edwards-3358329"><b>MOBO创始人Kanya King在奖项的新类型中 - “这感觉就像是正确的一年”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>庆祝《黑人原产》音乐的第27届年度仪式<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-mobos-heading-to-newcastle-first-time-2025-3799241">将首次在纽卡斯尔举行</a>。它将于2月18日星期二在该市的Utilita竞技场举行。</p><p>这些提名人于12月宣布，乔尔哈<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jorja-smith">·史密斯（</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jorja-smith">Jorja</a> Smith），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sampha">桑帕（Sampha</a> ），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bashy">巴西（Bashy</a> ），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ghetts">盖茨（Ghetts）</a> ，克莱奥·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cleo-sol">索尔（Cleo Sol）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">中央中央中央局（Central Cee）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/odeal">奥德尔（Edeal）</a>以三项提名领先。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mobo-awards-2025-see-the-full-list-of-nominees-3818607">在此处</a>查看完整列表。</p><p>现在，今年仪式上的第一波表演者已经揭示了Spice，他被提名为“最佳加勒比音乐法案”，即将登上舞台，以及Krept＆Konan。</p><p> Bashy还将表演，此前发行了他最近的专辑《贫穷的是昂贵》之后，获得了年度最佳专辑的提名，与前列腺癌的最佳男性表演和最佳嘻哈表演。该唱片是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bashy-on-being-poor-is-expensive-first-album-in-15-years-ididnt-know-whether-i-was-gonna-make-3773615-3773615">他15年来的第一个</a>，也以31名<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995">2024年最佳专辑</a>排名31。</p><p> MOBO创始人兼首席执行官Kanya King CBE说：“这些艺术家中的每位艺术家都为舞台带来了真正的特殊之处，这只是开始。从舞厅的充满活力到英国说唱和R＆B的动态声音，我们正在整理一个充满难忘时刻的夜晚。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFCqYFrM0p-/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658